      },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "content": "### Span metrics unavailable\n`traces_spanmetrics_*` and `traces_service_graph_*` returned empty vectors in this runner, so this dashboard keeps only Tempo-backed trace investigation paths.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Span Metrics Status",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
